Process called "get_module_name_from_path" that takes path as String returns String:
    Note: Extract module name from file path
    Let parts be split_path_with_separator with path as path
    Let filename be parts at index (length of parts minus1    Let name_parts be split_text_with_dot with text as filename
    Return name_parts at index0

Process called "get_module_path_from_file" that takes file_path as String returns OptionalString]:
    Note: Convert file path to module path
    If file_path ends with ".runa":
        Return file_path
    Otherwise:
        Return None

Process called "get_all_module_paths" that takes context as HotReloadContext returns List[String]:
    Let paths be list containing
    For each module_name in context.dependency_graph:
        Let node be context.dependency_graph[module_name]
        If node.file_path is not equal to ":          Add node.file_path to paths
    Return paths

Process calledget_oldest_cache_key that takes cache as Dictionary[String, Any] returns Optional[String]:
    Let oldest_key be None
    Let oldest_time be 9999999999
    
    For each key in cache:
        Let timestamp be cache[key]["timestamp"]
        If timestamp is less than oldest_time:
            Set oldest_time to timestamp
            Set oldest_key to key
    
    Return oldest_key

