Note: AI/Agent Integration
Process called "enable_ai_mode" that takes context as HotReloadContext returns None:
    Set context.config.ai_mode to true
    Set context.metadata["ai_enabled"] to true

Process calleddisable_ai_mode" that takes context as HotReloadContext returns None:
    Set context.config.ai_mode to false
    Set context.metadata["ai_enabled"] to false

Process called "get_ai_suggestions" that takes context as HotReloadContext and error as String returns ListString]:
    Note: AI-powered suggestions for fixing compilation errors
    Let suggestions be list containing
    If context.config.ai_mode:
        Add "Check syntax at line mentioned in error" to suggestions
        Add "Verify all imports are correct" to suggestions
        Add "Ensure all variables are properly declared" to suggestions
    Return suggestions 